<section class="bc-real-home">
  <div class="bc-hero">
    <p class="bc-kicker">Brian &amp; Co</p>

    <h1>Guidance, Resources, and Opportunities Presented With Care, Clarity, and Respect.</h1>

    <p class="bc-lead">
      We are pleased that you are here.
    </p>

    <p class="bc-lead">
      Brian &amp; Co was established with the belief that thoughtful guidance, carefully considered resources,
      and meaningful opportunities should be presented with dignity, clarity, and genuine regard for the individuals
      they are intended to serve.
    </p>

    <p class="bc-lead">
      Whether you are seeking greater preparedness, professional insight, accessibility accommodations,
      support for those you care about, or recommendations aligned with your interests and priorities,
      we endeavor to provide an experience guided by attentiveness, stewardship, and respect.
    </p>

    <p class="bc-lead">
      Every recommendation, resource, and opportunity presented through Brian &amp; Co is intended to be useful,
      understandable, and worthy of the confidence placed in it.
    </p>

    <div class="bc-hero-actions">
      <a href="#bc-offerings">Discover What Has Been Prepared for You</a>
      <a href="#bc-accessibility-concierge">Share What Would Be Most Meaningful Today</a>
      <a href="/account">Your Place Within Brian & Co</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="bc-offerings" class="bc-feature-grid">
    <article>
      <h2>Carefully Considered Offerings</h2>
      <p>
        Brian &amp; Co presents resources and offerings selected with the intention of supporting refined living,
        preparedness, comfort, usefulness, gifting, professional needs, and the many personal priorities that shape daily life.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Personalized Guidance &amp; Discovery</h2>
      <p>
        Rather than asking every visitor to navigate alone, Brian &amp; Co invites you to describe what would be most helpful,
        then presents thoughtful recommendations, relevant resources, and clearer next steps where available.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Ongoing Resources, Memberships &amp; Digital Experiences</h2>
      <p>
        Preparedness AI+, Business Intelligence AI+, Executive Concierge, accessibility support, and role-specific resources
        are being developed as refined pathways for ongoing assistance, education, and practical support.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Stewardship, Review &amp; Accountability</h2>
      <p>
        Protected access, complimentary considerations, professional relationships, public-facing changes, and important digital
        experiences remain guided by Brian’s review and green-check authorization standards.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <section class="bc-showcase">
    <div>
      <p class="bc-kicker">A More Considered Experience</p>
      <h2>Thoughtfully organized recommendations, presented as one Brian &amp; Co experience.</h2>
      <p>
        Brian &amp; Co works to bring together carefully considered offerings, trusted assistance, digital resources,
        and concierge-guided pathways while preserving a consistent standard of clarity, dignity, accessibility, and care.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bc-showcase-card">
      <strong>Areas of Interest Often Explored by Those We Serve</strong>
      <span>Home, Lifestyle &amp; Everyday Refinement</span>
      <span>Household Preparedness, Continuity &amp; Peace of Mind</span>
      <span>Professional Insight &amp; Business Support</span>
      <span>Accessibility, Caregiving &amp; Personal Well-Being</span>
      <span>Gift-Worthy Recommendations Chosen With Care</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bc-membership-strip">
    <p class="bc-kicker">Brian &amp; Co Intelligence</p>
    <h2>Personalized guidance, ongoing memberships, and carefully developed digital experiences.</h2>

    <div class="bc-mini-grid">
      <div>Preparedness AI+</div>
      <div>Executive Concierge</div>
      <div>Business Intelligence AI+</div>
      <div>Accessibility Concierge</div>
      <div>Professional Relationships &amp; Collaborative Pathways</div>
      <div>A Dedicated Space Prepared for Your Ongoing Experience</div>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

<style>
.bc-real-home{
  padding:clamp(28px,5vw,78px) 18px;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 75% 0%,rgba(242,201,92,.22),transparent 30%),
    linear-gradient(135deg,#020202 0%,#11100e 46%,#2c2415 100%);
  color:#fff7df;
}
.bc-hero,.bc-showcase,.bc-membership-strip{
  max-width:1220px;
  margin:0 auto 24px;
  border:1px solid rgba(242,201,92,.48);
  border-radius:34px;
  padding:clamp(28px,5vw,62px);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(5,5,5,.92),rgba(31,24,13,.90));
  box-shadow:0 32px 110px rgba(0,0,0,.46);
}
.bc-kicker{
  letter-spacing:.24em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:#f2c95c;
  font-size:12px;
  margin:0 0 14px;
}
.bc-hero h1{
  font-family:Georgia,serif;
  font-size:clamp(42px,7vw,84px);
  line-height:.98;
  max-width:1080px;
  margin:0 0 22px;
  color:#fff7df;
  text-shadow:0 0 28px rgba(242,201,92,.22);
}
.bc-lead,.bc-showcase p{
  font-size:19px;
  line-height:1.82;
  max-width:960px;
  color:rgba(255,247,223,.86);
}
.bc-hero-actions{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:12px;
  margin-top:30px;
}
.bc-hero-actions a{
  text-decoration:none;
  color:#fff7df;
  border:1px solid rgba(242,201,92,.62);
  border-radius:999px;
  padding:14px 18px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c160e,#6d5422);
}
.bc-feature-grid{
  max-width:1220px;
  margin:0 auto 24px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
  gap:16px;
}
.bc-feature-grid article,.bc-showcase-card{
  border:1px solid rgba(242,201,92,.38);
  border-radius:26px;
  padding:24px;
  background:rgba(5,5,5,.72);
  box-shadow:0 20px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
}
.bc-feature-grid h2,.bc-showcase h2,.bc-membership-strip h2{
  font-family:Georgia,serif;
  color:#fff7df;
  font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,48px);
  line-height:1.08;
  margin:0 0 14px;
}
.bc-feature-grid p{
  color:rgba(255,247,223,.82);
  line-height:1.76;
}
.bc-showcase{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.25fr) minmax(280px,.75fr);
  gap:24px;
  align-items:center;
}
.bc-showcase-card strong{
  display:block;
  color:#f2c95c;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.bc-showcase-card span,.bc-mini-grid div{
  display:block;
  margin:10px 0;
  padding:12px 14px;
  border:1px solid rgba(242,201,92,.28);
  border-radius:16px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
}
.bc-mini-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(210px,1fr));
  gap:12px;
}
@media(max-width:800px){
  .bc-showcase{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Brian Home",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Brian Home"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}





